Author: gorbise
Title: GREENEUM Pre-sale and ICO is coming!
Body: GREENEUM plans to accelerate the global energy transition from fossil fuels towards Solar and Renewable (GREEN) energy using smart contracts, targeted artificial intelligence and blockchain technology.  During the past two years at Greeneum, our team has been developing and perfecting the Greeneum technology and we are now ready to share it with the world.  The Greeneum Network is a platform that integrates blockchain technology, artificial intelligence (AI), machine learning and smart contracts to systematically improve the renewable energy market.  Updated Greeneum website - https://www.greeneum.net/  Token Pre-sale and ICO information - https://www.greeneum.net/contribute/  Check out our informational video - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uXDmWa8AhPc  Join our whiltelist! - https://www.greeneum.net/contribute/  Please ask our team any questions that you may have as we gear up for the ICO!
